text: KF Gradec (, FK Gradec) is a football club based in the village of Gradec near Gostivar, North Macedonia. They are currently competing in the OFS Gostivar league. ==History== The club was founded in 1977. ==References== ==External links== *Gradec Facebook *Club info at MacedonianFootball *Football Federation of Macedonia Gradec Category:Association football clubs established in 1977 Category:1977 establishments in the Socialist Republic of Macedonia Category:Gostivar Municipality Gradec
